name: Michael Peterson
profile_summary: The user is a 32-year-old man, stands 6'0" tall, straight sexuality, and identifies himself with He/Him/His pronouns. He is a white Caucasian, holds a graduate degree from UCLA, and works as a Software Engineer in the tech industry. Besides English, he also speaks Spanish. Currently settled in Los Angeles, he is originally from Boulder, Colorado. Honesty, respect, fitness, education, and friendship are his core values. His specific interests include hiking, coding, being a dog lover, traveling, and food. As an Atheist and politically liberal, he bears an MBTI Personality type of INTJ and star sign Aries. He owns a dog and does not have children but desires them in the future. He enjoys being active with occasional drinking, but refrains from smoking, marijuana, and other drugs. His intentions in dating are high, seeking long-term monogamous relationship.
